item.title: By: Anonymous
item.dc:creator: Anonymous
item.description: Radiohead don't do celebrity ass-kissing. Thom even declined an offer to collaborate with Sir Paul, with the lame excuse that he's too focused on his own music right now. Evidently Kanye felt slighted at the Grammys also. They never will fit in with the coporate mainstream set, although they have managed to sneak into the club as complete outsiders. I still can't figure out how they sell so well, when their music is so... smart, for lack of a better word.
item.content:encoded:
Radiohead don’t do celebrity ass-kissing. Thom even declined an offer to collaborate with Sir Paul, with the lame excuse that he’s too focused on his own music right now. Evidently Kanye felt slighted at the Grammys also.
They never will fit in with the coporate mainstream set, although they have managed to sneak into the club as complete outsiders. I still can’t figure out how they sell so well, when their music is so… smart, for lack of a better word.
